    "html": "<html lang=\"en-US\"><head>\n\t\t<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\n\t\t<title>VidSrc - Video Streaming API</title>\n\t\t<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Streaming link provider with auto-upgradable database and free access API.\">\n\t\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n\t\t<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\">\n\t\t<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"VidSrc - Video Streaming API\">\n\t\t<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"//i.imgur.com/9dH9RHB.jpg\">\n\t\t<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Streaming link provider with auto-upgradable database and free access API.\">\n\t\t<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://vidsrc.domains/\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://vidsrc.domains/\">\n\t\t<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index,follow\">\n\t\t\n\t\t<link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/4.5.3/css/bootstrap.min.css\" as=\"style\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.1/css/all.min.css\" as=\"style\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/styles.css?t=1760305935\" as=\"style\">\n\t\t\n        <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.0/jquery.min.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"\">\n        <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/2.5.4/umd/popper.min.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"\">\n        <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/4.5.3/js/bootstrap.min.js\" as=\"script\" crossorigin=\"\">\n        \n        <link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/vidsrc-ico.png?t=1688250921\">\n\t\t\n\t\t<link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/vidsrc-ico.png?t=1688250921\" type=\"image/x-icon\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/vidsrc-ico.png?t=1688250921\" type=\"image/x-icon\">\n\t\t\n\t\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/4.5.3/css/bootstrap.min.css\" integrity=\"sha512-oc9+XSs1H243/FRN9Rw62Fn8EtxjEYWHXRvjS43YtueEewbS6ObfXcJNyohjHqVKFPoXXUxwc+q1K7Dee6vv9g==\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.1/css/all.min.css\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/styles.css?t=1760305935\">\n\t</head>\n\t<body>\n\t\t<div class=\"content\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"logo\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/vidsrc-logo-light.svg?t=1688251159\" alt=\"VidSrc Logo\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"header\">\n\t\t\t\t<h1>VidSrc - Video Streaming API</h1>\n\t\t\t\t<p>Vidsrc offers streaming links for movies and episodes that can be effortlessly integrated into your website through embed links, API, or WordPress plugins.</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"main\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"bookmark-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Press Ctrl + D to bookmark this site to stay updated on Vidsrc domains.</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"m-list\">\n\t\t\t\t    <li><h3>NEW DOMAINS:</h3></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrcme.ru\">vidsrcme.ru<span class=\"live-text\">Live</span><span class=\"dot\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrcme.su\">vidsrcme.su<span class=\"live-text\">Live</span><span class=\"dot\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc-me.ru\">vidsrc-me.ru<span class=\"live-text\">Live</span><span class=\"dot\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc-me.su\">vidsrc-me.su<span class=\"live-text\">Live</span><span class=\"dot\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc-embed.ru\">vidsrc-embed.ru<span class=\"live-text\">Live</span><span class=\"dot\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc-embed.su\">vidsrc-embed.su<span class=\"live-text\">Live</span><span class=\"dot\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vsrc.su\">vsrc.su<span class=\"live-text\">Live</span><span class=\"dot\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><h3>OLD DOMAINS:</h3></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc.me\">vidsrc.me<span class=\"live-text\">Old, Use NEW</span><span class=\"doty\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"/\">vidsrc.in<span class=\"live-text\">Dead</span><span class=\"dotr\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"/\">vidsrc.net<span class=\"live-text\">Dead</span><span class=\"dotr\"></span></a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"https://vidsrc.pm\">vidsrc.pm<span class=\"live-text\">Dead</span><span class=\"dotr\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"/\">vidsrc.xyz<span class=\"live-text\">Dead</span><span class=\"dotr\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc.io\">vidsrc.io<span class=\"live-text\">Old, Use NEW</span><span class=\"doty\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc.vc\">vidsrc.vc<span class=\"live-text\">Dead</span><span class=\"dotr\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc.bz\">vidsrc.bz<span class=\"live-text\">Old, Use NEW</span><span class=\"doty\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc.gd\">vidsrc.gd<span class=\"live-text\">Old, Use NEW</span><span class=\"doty\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc.do\">vidsrc.do<span class=\"live-text\">Old, Use NEW</span><span class=\"doty\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"/\">vidsrc.mn<span class=\"live-text\">Dead</span><span class=\"dotr\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://vidsrc.tw\">vidsrc.tw<span class=\"live-text\">Old, Use NEW</span><span class=\"doty\"></span></a></li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mt-5\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>There can be other Vidsrc fake sites.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>They may steal your information or provide a bad user experience. Any Vidsrc site that is not listed above is fake, please do not use them.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>For more details about the real Vidsrc, you can contact their support team here:</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://vidsrc.community\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"support-link\"><i class=\"fab fa-telegram\"></i> Community Forum</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"footer\"><span>© Vidsrc</span></div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.0/jquery.min.js\" integrity=\"sha512-3gJwYpMe3QewGELv8k/BX9vcqhryRdzRMxVfq6ngyWXwo03GFEzjsUm8Q7RZcHPHksttq7/GFoxjCVUjkjvPdw==\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"></script>\n\t\t<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/2.5.4/umd/popper.min.js\" integrity=\"sha512-7yA/d79yIhHPvcrSiB8S/7TyX0OxlccU8F/kuB8mHYjLlF1MInPbEohpoqfz0AILoq5hoD7lELZAYYHbyeEjag==\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"></script>\n\t\t<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/4.5.3/js/bootstrap.min.js\" integrity=\"sha512-8qmis31OQi6hIRgvkht0s6mCOittjMa9GMqtK9hes5iEQBQE/Ca6yGE5FsW36vyipGoWQswBj/QBm2JR086Rkw==\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"></script>\n\t<script defer=\"\" src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v833ccba57c9e4d2798f2e76cebdd09a11778172276447\" integrity=\"sha512-57MDmcccJXYtNnH+ZiBwzC4jb2rvgVCEokYN+L/nLlmO8rfYT/gIpW2A569iJ/3b+0UEasghjuZH/ma3wIs/EQ==\" data-cf-beacon=\"{&quot;version&quot;:&quot;2024.11.0&quot;,&quot;token&quot;:&quot;3df50adc897b41d48e4045c210d51509&quot;,&quot;r&quot;:1,&quot;server_timing&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:{&quot;cfCacheStatus&quot;:true,&quot;cfEdge&quot;:true,&quot;cfExtPri&quot;:true,&quot;cfL4&quot;:true,&quot;cfOrigin&quot;:true,&quot;cfSpeedBrain&quot;:true},&quot;location_startswith&quot;:null}}\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\n\n</body></html>",
